Detailed Description

The Gui Class which sends commands to OnboardNodeHandler through GuiCommandMessages. It shows the states of various modes using check boxes and has buttons for commands without states. The Gui Class updates the checkboxes based on user inputs and also based on inputs from OnboardNodeHandler.

Subscribers:

  • /gui_state(rqt_quadcoptergui::GuiStateMessage): input state message coming from OnboardNodeHandler.
  • /quad_status(std_msgs::String): Message informing the state of quadrotor and various sensor data etc

Publishers:

  • /gui_commands(rqt_quadcoptergui::GuiCommandMessage): send commands to OnboardNodeHandler using this topic
